reviews.text: Booked reservations in celebration for Mother's Day! This restaurant doesn't accept phone reservations, required a deposit of HK$300 in advance which had to be paid down at the restaurant. I Highly do not recommend this restaurant to anyone, definitely will not be going back to this newly opened restaurant. Food quality was really bad...too salty & oily, portions were small and the service was appallingly! Bad attitude & rudeness from waitress. Usually I'd tip on top of the restaurants 10% service charge, but no way should I be required to tip for such bad service! Only booked there cause I heard good things but after tonight's dinner...NEVER AGAIN!

reviews.text: 食物質素同服務態度都唔錯，燒乳豬搭配小饅頭確係創新，減少乳豬嘅肥膩感。其次蒸魚、炒菜等都做得相當出色，確係有D驚喜。
冷氣好涷，要帶多件衫才好來啊！
海翩滙的海港能保持水准，早午夜市都抵食夾大件，值得稱讚！
食物質素，十分惡劣， 點心不斷翻蒸， 服務質素差劣， 十張枱有五張都投訴，食物像廚餘一樣，慘不忍睹， 有圖有真相， 咁都拎得出嚟畀人食， 正仆街
